## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on the topic. Some sources may have inherent biases, particularly those from opinion pieces or advocacy groups. Additionally, the cultural and legal context of divorce varies significantly across different regions, which may affect the generalizability of the findings. Further research is needed to explore the long-term societal impacts of legalizing divorce in various contexts.